# FILE: auth/login.desc
# ROLE: Unified Authentication Entry Gate
# ROUTE: /auth/login
# THEME: Dark · centered card · gradient accent

## DESIGN
- PAGE BG: dot-bg + radial glow behind card
- CARD: max-w-md mx-auto · bg-[#0F1828] · rounded-3xl · border border-[#1E2D45] · p-10
- LOGO: centered "ح" icon + "حلب يونيفر" at top of card

## 1. LOGIN FORM
- EMAIL INPUT: bg-[#162032] · border-[#1E2D45] · focus:border-[#6366F1] · text-[#F1F5F9]
- PASSWORD INPUT: same style + show/hide toggle
- REMEMBER ME: checkbox (styled with accent color)
- SUBMIT: full-width gradient-bg button "تسجيل الدخول"

## 2. ACCOUNT TYPE ROUTING (Post-Login)
- accountType === 'admin'    → redirect to /admin
- accountType === 'business' → redirect to /business
- accountType === 'student'  → redirect to /dashboard

## 3. BOTTOM LINKS
- "ليس لديك حساب؟" → /auth/register
- "نسيت كلمة المرور؟" → /auth/forgot-password

## 4. AUTH CONTEXT
- On successful login: populate AuthContext with { id, name, email, accountType, businessType?, isVerified, isFreelancer, xp, level, status }
- Store token in localStorage / sessionStorage
